      "content": "thanks for the list. i noticed you mentioned wake county areas like cary and apex. i've heard a lot about those being really nice, but i also know some people say the more diverse or urban parts of nc can be a bit more unpredictable school-wise. just being honest, i really want to avoid any areas where there might be social unrest or a lot of crime risk. are there certain districts you'd suggest staying away from to make sure we stay in those safer, more stable neighborhoods?",
